short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: An extension that makes it more convenient to set the scoresheet to the starting score.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: An extension that makes it more convenient to set the scoresheet to the starting score. This tool can be used by referees at the table when they are scoring teams. Press Control-Shift-0 on Windows or Command-Shift-0 on a Mac to reset the score sheet.
